      <textAnnotation id="sid-87816816-E0CD-4F3F-8335-00EA1700FA9A" signavio:alignment="left">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioDictionaryLink propertyId="name">
               <signavio:dictionaryLink>/glossary/cba70220b3344a51ae312020280ea644</signavio:dictionaryLink>
            </signavio:signavioDictionaryLink>
            <signavio:signavioType dataObjectType="IT-System"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bgcolor" metaValue="#e1e1e1"/>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>GraphiteConnect</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-A7A2205B-C68F-4A6A-B1DA-16CC5A33BBE0" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Commodity specific manual inputs-spreadsheets, power points</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-5142449E-CE8F-4199-A6C9-1C1383926255" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Process Tower: PTP - Procure To Pay
Process Group: PM - Procure Materials and Services (Direct &amp; Indirect)
Process: PM-050-170 Identify Approved Supplier</text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-829E01E9-4096-4BA6-A662-C5310D521632" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>To 'identify approved suppliers' means to recognize and select suppliers who have been evaluated and verified to meet specific standards set by a company. Analyze historic supplier evaluation data to determine which supplier performed to previously established standards and requirements .Prepare to issue request for quotation (RFQ) to identify supplier. </text>
      </textAnnotation>
      <textAnnotation id="sid-DA9645AB-4ED5-480D-9245-F523F73C629F" signavio:alignment="left" textFormat="text/plain">
         <extensionElements>
            <signavio:signavioMetaData metaKey="bordercolor" metaValue="#000000"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-left"/>
            <signavio:signavioLabel bold="" fill="#ff0000" fontFamily="" fontSize="" italic="" ref="text-right"/>
         </extensionElements>
         <text>Flow has been migrated to BIC. Please inform the process steward Nageswaran, Rohan &lt;rohan.nageswaran@intel.com&gt; and BPM Champions D'Elia, Traci &lt;traci.delia@intel.com&gt;,Newman, Jennifer &lt;jennifer.newman@intel.com&gt;of any design changes that occur within the flow moving forward. This will enable us to reflect those changes in the BIC and WIKI business process documentation.</text>
      </textAnnotation>
   </process>
